Reasoning: The paper deals with the design of constellations for coherent fiber-optical communication systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and communication theory (cs.COMM). The study of nonlinear phase noise (NLPN) is related to optics (cs.PHYS) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The optimization of constellations for different input power and fiber length involves optimization and heuristics (cs.OH).
